  "detailed_description": "WWIII has ended in total annihilation but the battle continues in outer space. Challenge 1-3 friends in the fast-paced & frantic arenas of Zero-G Gunfight. Pickup different guns that change how you move & fight. Dodge enemy bullets & avoid unique hazards as you strive to be the last one standing!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312060/extras/1c9474992420fd27afb5a35e9d2bd0ce.poster.avif?t=1678817940\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312060/extras/1c9474992420fd27afb5a35e9d2bd0ce.webm?t=1678817940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312060/extras/1c9474992420fd27afb5a35e9d2bd0ce.mp4?t=1678817940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Decades of a fragile peace are gone, the weapons of war are being mobilized as even the vastness of space is not big enough for peace.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312060/extras/c3c981251cb2f2bda7b3220dfabceea0.poster.avif?t=1678817940\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312060/extras/c3c981251cb2f2bda7b3220dfabceea0.webm?t=1678817940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312060/extras/c3c981251cb2f2bda7b3220dfabceea0.mp4?t=1678817940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Prepare yourself for the fast paced arenas of Zer0-G Gunfight where only the best will survive and bring their nation one set closer to intergalactic supremacy!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312060/extras/3702ae9d55d052017852c58ae21c2753.poster.avif?t=1678817940\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312060/extras/3702ae9d55d052017852c58ae21c2753.webm?t=1678817940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312060/extras/3702ae9d55d052017852c58ae21c2753.mp4?t=1678817940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br>2-4 player local PvP<br>Single Player Time Trail<br>Unique Arenas<br>Guns change they way you move and fight<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312060/extras/2cd6cf126fa1257a14ab85a8b298c8db.poster.avif?t=1678817940\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312060/extras/2cd6cf126fa1257a14ab85a8b298c8db.webm?t=1678817940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1312060/extras/2cd6cf126fa1257a14ab85a8b298c8db.mp4?t=1678817940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
